<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

 <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">Olympiad Preparation</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Courses</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">Olympiad</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


<section class="course-intro-creative">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-grid">
            <div class="intro-main">
                <span class="section-tag">Global Excellence</span>
                <h2 class="creative-heading">Achieve Your Full Potential in <span class="highlight">Olympiads</span></h2>
                <p class="creative-desc">
                    At Agrim Classes, we are committed to helping young minds achieve their full potential and excel in national and international Olympiads. We provide expert guidance to students preparing for various Olympiad exams, offering comprehensive support throughout their journey. Our institute is known for its dedication to fostering academic excellence.
                </p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i> Personalized Mentorship</h4>
                    <p>
                        Our experienced educators offer personalized mentorship, helping students navigate the complexities of Olympiad exams with confidence. The curriculum is meticulously designed to cover all essential topics, from foundational concepts to advanced problem-solving techniques.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-features">
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-cubes"></i></div>
                    <h5>Foundation Course</h5>
                    <p>Tailored for students transitioning from Class 9 to 10, laying a solid academic foundation for Olympiad preparation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
                    <h5>Intensive Regular Course</h5>
                    <p>Designed for higher grades to thoroughly prepare them for national and international Olympiads, focusing on logical reasoning and analytical thinking.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="boosters-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px; padding-top: 60px;">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="main-heading">Exam Preparation Boosters</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="boosters-grid">
            <div class="booster-card card-red">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i></div>
                <h4>India's Best<br>Ever Team</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-green">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                <h4>Small Batch Size<br>(Special 20)</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                <h4>Doubt Clearing<br>Session</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="far fa-building"></i></div>
                <h4>Complete Study Package<br>(Online | Offline)</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
                <h4>Fortnight<br>Test</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="eligibility-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
        <h3 class="table-title">Olympiad Eligibility & Details</h3>
        
        <div class="table-wrapper">
            <table class="eligibility-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th class="th-criteria">Eligibility criteria</th>
                        <th class="th-details">Details</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Academic Qualifications</td>
                        <td>Students from Class 1 to Class 12 can participate in various Olympiads based on subjects like Mathematics, Science, English, Computer Science, and General Knowledge.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Subjects Required</td>
                        <td>Depends on the Olympiad: Mathematics, Science, English, Cyber, General Knowledge, Astronomy, etc.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Age limit</td>
                        <td>No strict age limit, but students must be enrolled in Class 1 to 12.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Minimum Marks in Class 12</td>
                        <td>No specific marks required, but a good academic record is recommended.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Number of Attempts</td>
                        <td>Students can attempt the Olympiad exams each academic year from Class 1 to 12.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">State of Eligibility</td>
                        <td>Open to all students across India and abroad (varies based on the Olympiad type).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Nationality</td>
                        <td>Indian and international students are eligible (some Olympiads allow NRIs, PIOs, and OCIs).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Important Considerations</td>
                        <td>Some Olympiads have different stages, such as school-level, zonal, national, and international rounds. Registration is usually done via schools or directly online.</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="course-cta text-center">
            <h3>Ready to compete at the International level?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start Olympiad Prep Today <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<my-footer></my-footer>


<script src="footer.js"></script>

</body>